---
import Layout from "~/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Section from "~/components/Section.astro";
import Hero from "~/components/Hero.astro";
import { Picture, Image } from "astro:assets";
import Badge from "~/components/Badge.astro";
import Button from "~/components/Button.astro";
import ButtonCallUs from "~/components/ButtonCallUs.astro";
import Grid from "~/components/Grid.astro";
import Heading from "~/components/Heading.astro";
import WideImage from "~/components/WideImage.astro";
import ReviewSlider from "~/components/ReviewSlider.astro";

// Images
import PizzaHero from "~/assets/images/pizza-hero.png";
import Pizza from "~/assets/images/pizza.png";
import Spaghetti from "~/assets/images/spaghetti.png";
import Fish from "~/assets/images/fish.png";
import DecorativeImage from "~/assets/images/pexels-shvetsa-5953523.jpg";
import reviewAuthors from "~/assets/images/review-authors.png";
import Dessert from "~/assets/images/dessert.png";
import Mussels from "~/assets/images/mussels2.png";
---

<Layout title="Home" pageTitle="Home" description="Welcome to our restaurant!">
	<Section class:list={"bg-white"}>
		<Hero>
			<div slot="hero-content-left" class="prose max-w-none max-lg:order-1">
				<Badge title="Selamat Datang" />
				<h1 class="font-black">Percetakan Kertas Profesional</h1>

				<p>
				   Jangan Salah Pilih Percetakan! Kami adalah percetakan kertas profesional yang siap membantu Anda dalam
				   mencetak berbagai jenis produk kertas berkualitas tinggi. Dengan pengalaman bertahun-tahun di industri ini,
				   kami memahami betul kebutuhan Anda akan produk cetakan yang berkualitas dan tepat waktu.	
				
				</p>

				<span class="text-brand-green font-medium">✔ Kami juga bisa mengantar</span>

			
				<div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-x-8">
					<Button url="/book">PESAN SEKARANG</Button>
					<ButtonCallUs />
				</div>
			</div>
			<div slot="hero-content-right">
				<Picture
					class:list={"mx-auto"}
					src={PizzaHero}
					height={600}
					formats={["avif", "webp"]}
					alt="A description of my image."
					loading={"eager"}
					fetchpriority={"high"}
				/>
			</div>
		</Hero>
	</Section>

	<WideImage image={DecorativeImage} alt="Just an image" class:list={"aspect-video lg:aspect-[16/6]"} />

	<Section class:list={"bg-white"}>
		<Heading>
			<h2 slot="heading-title" class="font-black text-brand-green h2">Produk Kami</h2>
			<p slot="heading-content">
				Produk kami adalah hasil dari proses cetak yang cermat dan berkualitas tinggi. Bahan baku terbaik untuk memastikan setiap produk yang kami hasilkan memenuhi standar
				kualitas yang tinggi.
			</p>
		</Heading>

		<Grid>
			<div slot="grid-content-1">
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center prose text-center">
					<Picture
						class:list={"not-prose w-full h-auto"}
						src={Pizza}
						formats={["avif", "webp"]}
						alt="A description of my image."
					/>
					<h3 class="h4 mt-0 font-black">	Pembatas Dokumen</h3>
					<p>
						Pembatas dokumen adalah alat yang sangat berguna untuk menjaga kerapihan dan keteraturan dokumen
						Anda. Dengan desain yang menarik dan fungsional, pembatas dokumen kami akan membantu Anda
						mengorganisir berkas-berkas penting dengan mudah.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div slot="grid-content-2">
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center prose text-center">
					<Picture
						class:list={"not-prose w-full h-auto"}
						src={Spaghetti}
						formats={["avif", "webp"]}
						alt="A description of my image."
					/>
					<h3 class="h4 mt-0 font-black">Note</h3>
					<p>
						Note adalah alat tulis yang sangat penting untuk mencatat informasi penting, ide-ide kreatif,
						atau sekadar menulis catatan harian. Dengan berbagai ukuran dan desain yang menarik, note kami
						siap menemani setiap langkah Anda.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div slot="grid-content-3">
				<div class="flex flex-col items-center prose text-center">
					<Picture
						class:list={"not-prose w-full h-auto"}
						src={Fish}
						formats={["avif", "webp"]}
						alt="A description of my image."
					/>
					<h3 class="h4 mt-0 font-black">Pasta &amp; Spaghetti</h3>
					<p>
						Pasta is a staple of Italian cuisine, with a rich history dating back centuries. It comes in
						various shapes and sizes, each suited to different sauces and preparations.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</Grid>
	</Section>

	<Section class:list={"bg-white"}>
		<Hero>
			<div slot="hero-content-left" class="prose lg:order-2">
				<h1 class="font-black">Mesin Cetak</h1>

				<p>
					Mesin cetak adalah alat yang digunakan untuk mencetak teks dan gambar pada berbagai media, seperti
					kertas, karton, dan plastik. Dengan teknologi terbaru, mesin cetak kami mampu menghasilkan cetakan
					yang tajam dan berkualitas tinggi.
				</p>

				<p>
					Mesin cetak kami dilengkapi dengan teknologi canggih yang memungkinkan kami untuk mencetak dengan
					cepat dan efisien. Kami juga memiliki berbagai jenis mesin cetak untuk memenuhi kebutuhan cetak
					Anda, mulai dari cetakan kecil hingga besar.
				</p>

				<div class="mt-8">
					<Button url="/menu">
						<svg
							xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
							viewBox="0 0 20 20"
							fill="currentColor"
							class="size-5 inline-block"
							aria-hidden="true"
						>
							<path
								fill-rule="evenodd"
								d="M8.22 5.22a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0l4.25 4.25a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-4.25 4.25a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06-1.06L11.94 10 8.22 6.28a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06Z"
								clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
						</svg>
						View menu
					</Button>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div slot="hero-content-right">
				<Picture
					class:list={"mx-auto"}
					src={PizzaHero}
					height={600}
					formats={["avif", "webp"]}
					alt="A description of my image."
				/>
			</div>
		</Hero>
	</Section>

	<Section class:list={"bg-white"}>
		<Hero>
			<div slot="hero-content-left" class="prose max-w-none max-lg:order-1">
				<Badge color="red" title="delicious" />
				<h2 class="font-black h2 !my-4">Plate of the week</h2>

				<span class="text-brand-red text-2xl font-bold italic">Fresh Mussels!</span>

				<p>
					Our plate of the week is a delicious dish that changes every week. This week, we're featuring fresh
					mussels cooked in a white wine and garlic sauce, served with a side of crispy fries. Don't miss out
					on this limited-time offer!
				</p>

				<div class="mt-8">
					<Button color="red" url="/book">Book now</Button>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div slot="hero-content-right">
				<Picture
					class:list={"mx-auto"}
					src={Mussels}
					height={600}
					formats={["avif", "webp"]}
					alt="A description of my image."
				/>
			</div>
		</Hero>
	</Section>

	<!-- Reviews -->
	<Section class="bg-brand-red/20 relative text-center">
		{/* Wrapper utama: flex row, center horizontal & vertical */}
		<div class="py-16 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-center min-h-[60vh]">
		  
		  {/* Bagian Penilaian Pelanggan */}
		  <div class="lg:w-1/2 px-6 mb-8 lg:mb-0">
			<Hero>
			  {/* Konten kiri (sebenarnya kini full-width karena text-center) */}
			  <div
				slot="hero-content-left"
				class="prose max-w-none text-center mx-auto"
			  >
				{/* Judul di tengah */}
				<h2
				  slot="heading-title"
				  class="font-black text-4xl mb-2"
				>
				  PENILAIAN PELANGGAN
				</h2>
				{/* Garis aksen di tengah */}
				<div class="w-16 h-1 bg-brand-red rounded mx-auto mb-6"></div>
	  
				{/* Paragraf di tengah, dibatasi lebar agar nyaman dibaca */}
				<div slot="heading-content">
				  <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 mx-auto max-w-xl">
					Kami selalu mengutamakan kepuasan pelanggan. Berikut beberapa
					ulasan klien kami tentang layanan percetakan berkualitas dari
					Grafika Printing Gemilang.
				  </p>
	  
				  {/* Slider benar-benar di tengah */}
				  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-md">
					<ReviewSlider />
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			</Hero>
		  </div>
	  
		  {/* Bagian Kerjasama Bisnis */}
		  <div class="lg:w-1/2 px-6">
			<Hero>
			  {/* Konten kanan */}
			  <div
				slot="hero-content-left"
				class="prose max-w-none text-center mx-auto"
			  >
				{/* Judul di tengah */}
				<h2
				  slot="heading-title"
				  class="font-black text-4xl mb-2"
				>
				  KERJASAMA BISNIS
				</h2>
				{/* Garis aksen di tengah */}
				<div class="w-16 h-1 bg-brand-blue rounded mx-auto mb-6"></div>
	  
				{/* Paragraf di tengah, dibatasi lebar agar nyaman dibaca */}
				<div slot="heading-content">
				  <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 mx-auto max-w-xl">
					Kami percaya bahwa kerjasama yang baik menghasilkan hasil yang luar biasa. 
					Berikut adalah beberapa mitra kami dari berbagai industri yang telah bekerja sama dengan kami dalam menyediakan layanan percetakan berkualitas.
				  </p>
	  
				  {/* Gallery atau daftar mitra */}
				  <div class="gap-8 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
					<div class="p-4 bg-white shadow rounded-md text-center">
						<Picture
						class:list={"not-prose w-full h-auto max-w-[500px] mx-auto"}
						src={reviewAuthors}
						formats={["avif", "webp"]}
						alt="A description of my image."
					/>
					  <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Perusahaan A</p>
					</div>
					<div class="p-4 bg-white shadow rounded-md text-center">
					  <img src="partner-logo-2.png" alt="Mitra 2" class="mx-auto mb-4 w-24 h-24 object-contain"/>
					  <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Perusahaan B</p>
					</div>
					{/* Tambahkan lebih banyak mitra sesuai kebutuhan */}
				  </div>
				</div>
			  </div>
			</Hero>
		  </div>
	  
		</div>
	  </Section>
	  
	<!-- Desserts -->
	<Section class:list={"bg-white"}>
		<Hero>
			<div slot="hero-content-left" class="prose max-w-none order-2">
				<Badge title="dolce" />
				<h2 slot="heading-title" class="font-black text-brand-green h2 !my-4">Desserts</h2>
				<div slot="heading-content">
					<p>
						Indulge in our selection of sweet treats, from classic tiramisu to decadent chocolate cake. Our
						desserts are the perfect way to end your meal on a high note.
					</p>

					<p>
						Experience the taste of Italy with our authentic dishes made from the finest ingredients.
						Indulge in our wide variety of pizzas, pastas, and desserts, all crafted with love and
						tradition. Whether you're dining in or taking out, we promise a memorable culinary experience.
					</p>

					<div class="mt-8">
						<Button url="/menu">See our menu</Button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div slot="hero-content-right">
				<Picture
					class:list={"mx-auto"}
					src={Dessert}
					height={600}
					formats={["avif", "webp"]}
					alt="A description of my image."
				/>
			</div>
		</Hero>
	</Section>

	<!-- Contact -->
	<Section class:list={"bg-white"}>
		<Hero>
			<div slot="hero-content-left" class="prose max-w-none">
				<Badge color="red" title="benvenuto" />
				<h2 slot="heading-title" class="font-black text-brand-red h2 !my-4">Drop by and say hello</h2>
				<div slot="heading-content">
					<p>
						We're located in the heart of the city, just a stone's throw away from the main square. Our
						restaurant is the perfect place to enjoy a delicious meal with friends and family.
					</p>

					<span class="text-brand-red font-medium">
						✔ We also do take-away, so you can enjoy your food at home
					</span>

					<div class="mt-8">
						<Button color="red" url="/book">Book a table</Button>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div slot="hero-content-right">
				<Picture
					class:list={"mx-auto"}
					src={Dessert}
					height={600}
					formats={["avif", "webp"]}
					alt="A description of my image."
				/>
			</div>
		</Hero>
	</Section>
</Layout>
